    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Collation: 11 unfoliated leaves; 1⁸ + 3 leaves tipped to stubs; catchwords each verso, lower left.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Layout: 17 long lines; ruled with a misṭarah.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Script: Written in neat naskh in black ink; pointed, partially vocalized.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Decoration: Rubrications in red.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Binding: Unbound; remains of textile around the spine.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Origin: Copy is undated; perhaps copied in the 17th or 18th century.</subfield>
    </datafield>
